<h2><a href="http://uwnews.org/relatedcontent/2010/March/rc_parentID56284_thisID56367.pdf">DMP: Deterministic Shared Memory Multiprocessing</a></h2>
		<p>Current shared memory multicore and multiprocessor systems are nondeterministic.In this paper, the authors make the case for fully deterministic shared memory multiprocessing (DMP).</p>

